data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS. Open concept rancher in Corryton on a cul-de-sac! Freshly painted and brand new LVP flooring!! Charming 3 bed, 2 bath one level rancher, stainless steel appliances with large living room and garage, vaulted ceilings, back deck with new deck boards leading into a pleasant, level yard complete with a peach tree! Eat in kitchen with an expansive bay window, large main bedroom in a walkable, quiet, family friendly neighborhood facing the open Tennessee countryside!
